Package jade.core.messaging

Interface MessagingSlice

All Superinterfaces:
Serializable, Service.Slice
All Known Implementing Classes:
MessagingProxy
public interface MessagingSlice extends Service.Slice
The horizontal interface for the JADE kernel-level service managing the message passing subsystem installed in the platform.
Author:
Giovanni Rimassa - FRAMeTech s.r.l.
